                        <p class="placename">
                Vilnius Ghetto<br /><span class="alt">(Vilna Ghetto, <br /><span class="alt">(Wilno Ghetto)</span>
            </p>
                                    <p class="municipality">
                <strong>Location:</strong>
                Vilnius, Lithuania<br />
                            </p>
                            <div>
                Established in 1941, this ghetto was closed  in the summer of 1943 and its survivors went to the Riga-Kaiserwald concentration camp.
            </div>
